```css
* {
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

article {
    position: relative;
    padding: 10px;
    padding-left: 220px;
    height: 220px;
    background: red;
}

article .image {
    position: absolute;
    left: 10px;
    top: 10px;
    background: #000;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
}

article .content {
    width: 100%;
}
```

